## Project Structure

- **Ticket storage**: `.flux/` (in-repo) or `.flux-store/` (orphan mode with git worktree)
- **Board config**: `config.json` in the active flux directory (read via `get_board_config`)
- **Project docs**: `.docs/` ‚Äî READ THESE before implementation work
- **Skill modules**: `.claude/rules/event-horizon.md` ‚Äî reference for workflows and tool details

