## File Access Boundaries

**Read & Write Freely:**
- `engine/src/` ‚Äî backend logic
- `portal/src/` ‚Äî frontend components
- `.docs/` ‚Äî project documentation
- Any other source code directories

**Read Only:**
- All sibling repos in multi-repo projects (never edit them ‚Äî author in the parent repo's `.flux-group/`)

**Never Touch:**
- `.flux/` ‚Äî ticket files (in-repo mode)
- `.flux-store/` ‚Äî ticket files (orphan mode)
- `.flux/config.json` ‚Äî use `get_board_config` MCP tool instead

